how do i train my dog to come when i calll him the first thing your dog needs to learn it his name you say the dogs name and when he looks at you give him a treat never scold your dog using his or her name that should only be for good things once he learns his name the best way to teach him to come to you is to squat down to his level open your arms say his name with the command come that gives him something exciting to go to when he does come to you praise him and give him treats also never punish your dog after he comes to you or he will start to associate coming to you with bad things always use an excited voice and remember even if you are mad at him if he comes to you when you tell him to he did the right thing and should be praised for it Dog agility Housebreaking Obedience training Reinforcement Humphrey Bogart Abu Ghraib torture and prisoner abuse Main characters of Fullmetal Alchemist Clicker training Social rule Piccolo Junior Saga Singlish Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban Inspector Gadget Le Malade imaginaire Dean Koontz Obi-Wan Kenobi Socrates A Course In Miracles Kender Utilitarianism Logic Chesapeake Bay Retriever Musical Canine Freestyle The Price Is Right Kim Possible Theory of conduct Childbirth The Legend of Zelda: Majora's Mask Ten Commandments Black comedy 1957 World Series Gun dog Into the West (miniseries) Merit Scientology beliefs and practices Dogsled racing Shaggy dog story Family Guy Goodness and value theory Comparing and contrasting Judaism and Christianity Great Ape language Hearing impairment John the Baptist Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Witches (Discworld) Conditioning Hansel und Gretel Reincarnation The nature of God in Western theology Great Teacher Onizuka Eutheism, dystheism, and maltheism Brian Griffin Avenue Q Schutzhund Animal Farm Martial art Robert De Niro Confucius Air Education and Training Command English grammar Power Rangers: SPD The Life and Times of Juniper Lee John Howard Yoder Force (Star Wars